Constantcontact
===============

Using ConstantContact (CC) API in your Rails Apps


Installation
============
Inside your Rails App, do

ruby script/plugin install git@github.com:pash/constantcontact.git


Example
=======
1) Initialize
cc = ConstantContact::Connect.new(username, password, key)

2) Get CC Contacts
cc.get_contacts

3) GET CC Campaigns
cc.get_campaigns(STATUS)

STATUS can be 'DRAFT', 'SENT', 'RUNNING' or 'SCHEDULED'


